In [[surfing]], a '''point break''' is where a [[wave]] breaks as it hits a point of land jutting out from the coastline. Waves break in a variety of ways, the other main types (for surfers) being a [[reef break]] and a [[beach break]].

----

'''''[[Point Break (movie)|Point Break]]''''' is also a film starring [[Patrick Swayze]] and [[Keanu Reeves]] and the name of a short-lived [[United Kingdom|British]] [[boyband]].

